#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The stub class names are derived from the service name used in your `proto` file.\n"
"For example, if you use `Greeter` as a service name as in:"
msgstr "存根类的名称源自您在 `proto` 文件中使用的服务名称。例如，如果您像下面这样使用 `Greeter` 作为服务名称："

#. type: Plain text
