msgstr "请查阅 link:https://grpc.github.io/grpc-java/javadoc/io/grpc/ClientInterceptor.html[ClientInterceptor] 的 link:https://grpc.github.io/grpc-java/javadoc/io/grpc/ClientInterceptor.html[JavaDoc] ，以正确实现您的拦截器。"

